~eGNGB Controls~0
  Enter       -  Start
  Right Shift - Select
  W           - B Button
  X           - A Button
  TAB         - Open menu
  F9          - fullscreen on/off
  F10         - show fps
  F11         - reset
  F12         - show keysym code
  KeyPad 1-5  - Change palette
  KeyPad 6    - Toggle color filter
